div.div:
When autopilot is active, takes the position of the aircraft and calculates appropriate actions. When autopilot is inactive, takes the controller inputs from the receiver.
Data is then passed to the Flight Controller.
Arguments:
- Instrument Positional Data
- Autopilot Active Boolean
Log:
- PID Calculations
- Pitch, Roll, Yaw, Power
